class Jana: """ Creade class Jana with the attribute person """ attr1 = "person" count = 1

def replicate(self, times=1):
    Jana.count *= 2**times
    print("There are now ", Jana.count)
def restart(self):
    Jana.count = 1
    print("We're back to", Jana.count, Jana.attr1)
